#: ../../docs/classes/class_parallaxlayer.rst:14
msgid ""
"A parallax scrolling layer to be used with :ref:`ParallaxBackground "
"<class_ParallaxBackground>`."
msgstr "要与 :ref:`ParallaxBackground <class_ParallaxBackground>` 一起使用的视差滚动层。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_parallaxlayer.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_parallaxlayer.rst:19
msgid ""
"A ParallaxLayer must be the child of a :ref:`ParallaxBackground "
"<class_ParallaxBackground>` node. Each ParallaxLayer can be set to move "
"at different speeds relative to the camera movement or the "
":ref:`ParallaxBackground.scroll_offset "
"<class_ParallaxBackground_property_scroll_offset>` value."
msgstr ""
"``ParallaxLayer`` 必须是 :ref:`ParallaxBackground "
"<class_ParallaxBackground>` 节点的子级。可以将每个 ``ParallaxLayer`` "
"设置为以不同的速度，相对于相机移动或设置为 :ref:`ParallaxBackground.scroll_offset "
"<class_ParallaxBackground_property_scroll_offset>` 值。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_parallaxlayer.rst:21
msgid "This node's children will be affected by its scroll offset."
msgstr "该节点的子节点，将受其滚动偏移量的影响。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_parallaxlayer.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Note:** Any changes to this node's position and scale made after it "
"enters the scene will be ignored."
msgstr "**注意**：进入场景后，对该节点的位置和比例，所做的任何更改都将被忽略。"

